{"tid":2439593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海峰花園再有住客染疫　58歲男光顧10間餐廳","createTime":"2021-03-09T11:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T16:01:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2d71f8597ee2f9932bacf93ecbb437da682daadf","tid":2439593,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"第二宗不明源頭初步確診個案為58歲男，在深水埗區醫局街怡高工業中心工作，住華景山路海峰花園一座，之前已有一名退休婦確診而列為強制檢測大廈，兩宗個案單位不同層數及方向。他由3月3日起不舒服，3月5日最後上班。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潛伏期光顧葵芳敏華冰廳、大澳金培餐廳<br />\n<br />\n他平時會與家人在附近餐廳食飯，潛伏期內足跡包括葵芳敏華冰廳、明珠宴會廳；平時早餐會到泰華食堂、長沙灣意樂餐廳、翡翠海鮮酒家、燉奶佬、頤東酒家、葵涌百份百餐廳、新世紀廣場的千兩、大澳的金培餐廳。另外，他曾與幾位朋友在華景山路打網球，與家人都須送檢疫中心。"},{"pid":"0fc34eccacc5fbd82749ec63aa219524909cc7e8","tid":2439593,"uid":54620,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"全藍餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49778e04dec593106167351806dbebbbccb81e2","tid":2439593,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"有安心出行，唔怕"},{"pid":"af0e5969cf3b2107fc465ae837acf91d51d8094f","tid":2439593,"uid":184261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0fc34eccacc5fbd82749ec63aa219524909cc7e8","tid":2439593,"uid":54620,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"全藍餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"武肺手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0a630c1590a18dc2aac77e9c956d508fabf6d8","tid":2439593,"uid":70439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"藍絲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc08d2ef1bc7413979d587bacfb8202919339f1d","tid":2439593,"uid":129466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0fc34eccacc5fbd82749ec63aa219524909cc7e8","tid":2439593,"uid":54620,"like":41,"dislike":0